      "**Pretraining = learned representations, not memorized facts** — 7B@1T ≠ 7B@100B, even after identical fine-tune.",
      "**Fine-tuning ≈ same distribution shift as domain pretraining** — at roughly 10⁵–10⁷× less compute.",
